## Appendix F: Dead Letter Resolution Procedure

```
1. Alert received: [!] Dead letter on {pipeline} event {event_id}
2. SELECT dl.*, e.* FROM dead_letter dl JOIN events e ON dl.event_id=e.id WHERE dl.resolved=false
3. Read error_message and payload
4. Fix the root cause
5. Log fix in /home_ai/.claude/decisions/issues-fixes-log.md
6. UPDATE events SET status='pending', retry_count=0, error_message=null WHERE id={event_id}
7. UPDATE dead_letter SET resolved=true, resolved_at=NOW(), resolution_notes='...' WHERE event_id={event_id}
8. Monitor n8n for successful processing
```

